  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694290/extras/2ae17d46859b0a4d370a23e832e3dc09.poster.avif?t=1762937119\" width=614 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694290/extras/2ae17d46859b0a4d370a23e832e3dc09.webm?t=1762937119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694290/extras/2ae17d46859b0a4d370a23e832e3dc09.mp4?t=1762937119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Grim Reaper's perfect vacations was interrupted. Zombies wants revenge and now all hell breaks loose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill the Reaper</strong> is a minimalistic survival game with roguelite elements.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight numerous zombies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock and customize various melee and ranged weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make special cocktails</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Level up and upgrade useful skills </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Survive as long as you can </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get highest score through advanced score system</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold back armies of the dead and find out, how long does it take to <strong>Kill the Reaper</strong>?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694290/extras/2ae17d46859b0a4d370a23e832e3dc09.poster.avif?t=1762937119\" width=614 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694290/extras/2ae17d46859b0a4d370a23e832e3dc09.webm?t=1762937119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694290/extras/2ae17d46859b0a4d370a23e832e3dc09.mp4?t=1762937119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Grim Reaper's perfect vacations was interrupted. Zombies wants revenge and now all hell breaks loose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill the Reaper</strong> is a minimalistic survival game with roguelite elements.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight numerous zombies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock and customize various melee and ranged weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make special cocktails</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Level up and upgrade useful skills </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Survive as long as you can </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get highest score through advanced score system</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold back armies of the dead and find out, how long does it take to <strong>Kill the Reaper</strong>?</p>",
